### Admin Subscriptions API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Variables
@subscriptionId = 1
@paymentId = 1

### ========== OVERVIEW & ANALYTICS ==========

### 1. Get Subscription Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get Subscription Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Subscription Analytics with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/analytics?start_date=2025-01-01&end_date=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Quick Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/quick-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== LISTS ==========

### 5. Get Operations Log
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/operations?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get Operations Log with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/operations?page=1&limit=20&subscription_id=1&operation_type=renew
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Upcoming Renewals (Next 7 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/upcoming-renewals?days=7&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Upcoming Renewals (Next 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/upcoming-renewals?days=30&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Failed Payments
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/failed-payments?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========== INDIVIDUAL OPERATIONS ==========

### 10. Manual Renewal
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/renew
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reason": "Manual renewal due to payment issue resolution"
}

### 11. Extend Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/extend
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "days": 30,
  "reason": "Customer service compensation"
}

### 12. Retry Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/retry
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reason": "Payment gateway issue resolved"
}

### 13. Pause Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/pause
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reason": "Customer requested temporary pause"
}

### 14. Cancel Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reason": "Customer requested cancellation"
}

### 15. Upgrade Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/upgrade
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "new_plan_id": 2,
  "reason": "Customer requested upgrade to Pro plan",
  "prorate": true
}

### 16. Sync Billing
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/sync-billing
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reason": "Billing cycle synchronization requested"
}

### ========== BULK OPERATIONS ==========

### 17. Bulk Action - Renew
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/bulk-action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "subscription_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "operation_type": "renew",
  "reason": "Bulk renewal after system maintenance"
}

### 18. Bulk Action - Extend
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/bulk-action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "subscription_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "operation_type": "extend",
  "reason": "Bulk extension for customer service",
  "metadata": {
    "days": 15
  }
}

### 19. Bulk Action - Retry Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/bulk-action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "subscription_ids": [4, 5, 6],
  "operation_type": "retry_payment",
  "reason": "Bulk payment retry after gateway fix"
}

### 20. Bulk Action - Pause
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/bulk-action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}{
  "subscription_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "operation_type": "pause",
  "reason": "Bulk pause for system maintenance"
}### 21. Bulk Action - Cancel
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/bulk-action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}{
  "subscription_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "operation_type": "cancel",
  "reason": "Bulk cancellation due to policy change"
}### 22. Bulk Action - Upgrade Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/bulk-action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}{
  "subscription_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "operation_type": "upgrade_plan",
  "reason": "Bulk upgrade to new tier",
  "metadata": {
    "new_plan_id": 2,
    "prorate": true
  }
}### 23. Bulk Action - Sync Billing
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/subscriptions/bulk-action
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}{
  "subscription_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "operation_type": "sync_billing",
  "reason": "Bulk billing synchronization"
}